{"tid":1417464,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實不如真係諗吓點樣動員罷買？","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:51:25.000Z","uid":37331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb43401e3235ba96ba13af6075ce59fa59d18725","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"無錯今晚勇武打走好多黑社會係好爽，癱瘓交通不合作運動亦好成功，但係勇武派幫大家打前線退敵同街頭抗爭嘅同時，不如大家都諗吓和理非有咩可以做去持續俾政府壓力？<br />\n<br />\n老實講就算我地日日遊行，一嚟可以動員嘅人未必每次都咁多，即時嘅影響亦始終有限，我覺得罷買係一樣門欖最低嘅行動，其實就好似杯葛cctvb 廣告商咁，商家佬利益受損就點都會出下聲，最好就係用呢樣嘢做籌碼去挾商家佬配合更有組織嘅罷工罷市，有無文宣同冷氣軍師諗吓實行嘅可能性？"},{"pid":"9efb31de8836fbeb503aecfa3d322429adb7a82c","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63fa184f3f0d7e21adb0e0cbb9a0b508b0c387b4","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"384f4db0657ce1666b98e58fb357bbf857b2a827","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"92dbc0a62e2cea2cb3eb3ed0121e49f0f41bac46","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a088663a4c6f115341a4a58a5621b8aef5ef94c0","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"272752e6f24245ad07ac9ff6ca53453df572d970","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1f2665d82f13fea23822f89926907e3535fc917e","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"609c5caec745d30e7dd1a27204b2b43b9de3d87e","tid":1417464,"uid":37331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a37228f23ddb1f5dfefa1fdd46c5f